<HEADLINE>
TEST YOUR LITERARY KNOWLEDGE
</HEADLINE>
 (For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
c.1999 Fort Worth Star-Telegram 
<TEXT>
<P>
   .MDNM/Here's another simple matching exercise, titles with their
authors. You pass with seven correct answers and attain an A with
nine right. Score yourself an extra point if you identify correctly
the one work that appeared before the present century.
</P>
<P>
   The variably literary works:
</P>
<P>
   1. ``The Day of Doom''.MDBU/.MDNM/
</P>
