   &UR; FINANCIAL (f) &LR;
</P>
<P>
   Y2K-AIRLINES (Undated) _ Airlines, FAA say they are prepared for
2000, noting that flying on Dec. 31 or Jan. 1 will be as safe as
today. By Matthew Brelis. 600 words.
