<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    BIPARTISAN HOUSE BILL WOULD PUNISH WORLD BANK FOR CONTROVERSIAL
TIBET LOAN
 &HT;    Moving in both (i) International and (w) Washington categories.
 &HT;    By JEFF NESMITH 
 &HT;    c.1999 Cox News Service(at) 
