<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-10-01 20:16 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A3999 &Cx1f; ttx-z
r f BC-CARS-WILLIAMS-COLUMN-     10-01 1317
