<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-10-01 20:17 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A4001 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u a BC-EX-MILITANT-RELEASE-B     10-01 1530
