<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-10-01 20:18 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A4004 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u s BC-BKO-CELTICS-GASTON-BO     10-01 0365
