<HEADLINE>
TEXAS GROUP CANCELS BUCHANAN APPEARANCES
</HEADLINE>
 (For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
By MAX B. BAKER 
c.1999 Fort Worth Star-Telegram 
<TEXT>
