QUOTATION OF THE DAY
</HEADLINE>
 (Eds.: This quotation refers to BC-IRAN-POLITICS-NYT, which moved
in ``i'' news file.) 
c.1999 N.Y. Times News Service   
<TEXT>
<P>
   ``In an Islamic system, punishment is the authorities'
prerogative. Any such act from any person is forbidden, and now
that I have forbidden it, it is not only legally barred but
religiously forbidden.''
</P>
<P>
   _AYATOLLAH ALI KHAMENEI of Iran.
</P>
